job description
overview
the primary goal of this software engineer will be to develop application that better integrate widespread distributed energy resource with the grid solarcity belief that smart management of these system will provide significant value to grid operator and energy market participant this engineer will be responsible for creating application that interface our energy optimization service with human and machine client over the web
